>> When does transfer learning work best between datasets A and B? <<

( ) When the model performs really well on dataset A {{ The performance of the model on dataset A does not guarantee good transfer learning}}
( ) When the size of dataset A and B is similar {{ The size of the datasets is irrelevant to the transfer learning performance }}
(x) When the domain of dataset B is similar to the domain of dataset A 
( ) When the model is small {{ The size of the model is irrelevant to the transfer learning performance}}
